title: Weir of Hermiston :
author: Stevenson, Robert Louis
snippet: And this is why there is a new household and a brand-new baby in Naseby Dower House; and why the great Van Tromp lives in pleasant style upon the shores of England; and why twenty-six individual copies of the Thymebury Star are received  daily at the door of Naseby House.
